動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/110%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c1409%2c20210927%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,110,審簡,1409,20210927,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"1409","JDATE":"20210927","JTITLE":"竊盜"}